premise_source_doc_sentence: The film has a framing story of Po the Dragon Warrior  (  in computer animation  )  telling the stories of his comrades in arms , the Furious Five , which are depicted in 2D cel animation , similar to the opening and end credits of the original film .

Secrets of the Furious Five  (  also known as Kung Fu Panda : Secrets of the Furious Five  )  is an American animated short produced by DreamWorks Animation , which serves as a semi-sequel or spin-off to the animated feature film Kung Fu Panda and appears on a companion disc of the original film 's deluxe DVD release .
Mary Wickes had voiced Laverne the gargoyle in the original film , but died during the release of the first film .
The first film was the only one to have a theatrical release ; the sequels , which were n't as well received as the original film , were released either direct to video or were made for television .
Tony Jay had voiced Judge Claude Frollo in the original film .
